      <h1 class='title'>Housing (Northern Ireland) Order 1981 (S.I 1981/156 (N.I. 3))</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='grand-committee-report-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 17 May 2004 vol 661 c321GC</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_321gc' title='Col. 321GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 May 2004 vol 661 c321GC' name='column_321gc' href='#column_321gc' rel='bookmark'>321GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04076'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_687' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        4 (1) Amend Article 2A (meaning of member of a person's family) as follows.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04077'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_688' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (2) In paragraph (1)(a)&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) after "spouse" insert "or civil partner", and</li>
        <li>(b) after "live together as husband and wife" insert "or as if they were civil partners".</li></ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04078'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_689' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (3) In paragraph (2)(a), after "a relationship by marriage" insert "or civil partnership".
      </p>
